 How to install Kalabox on Ubuntu

Debian/Ubuntu
Installation

    Download the .deb package from kalabox.io/download
    Double-click on the .deb package to launch Software Center
    Click the “Install” button and enter your password when prompted

If you do not have the GUI-based Software Center you can install the .deb pkg on the command line.

sudo apt-get update -y
sudo apt-get install bridge-utils iptables cgroup-bin
sudo dpkg -i kalabox.deb

